  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For other uses, see <a href=\"/index.php/Othgar_Hoare_(the_Soulless)\" title=\"Othgar Hoare (the Soulless)\">Othgar Hoare (the Soulless)</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Othgar_Hoare_(Demonlover)\" title=\"Othgar Hoare (Demonlover)\">Othgar Hoare (Demonlover)</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Hrothgar of Pyke</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nHrothgar of Pyke</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Age_of_Heroes\" title=\"Age of Heroes\">Age of Heroes</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Pyke_(island)\" title=\"Pyke (island)\">Pyke</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Hrothgar of Pyke</b> was a legendary <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> raider from <a href=\"/index.php/Pyke_(island)\" title=\"Pyke (island)\">Pyke</a> who supposedly lived during the <a href=\"/index.php/Age_of_Heroes\" title=\"Age of Heroes\">Age of Heroes</a>. He possessed a <a href=\"/index.php/Horn\" title=\"Horn\">horn</a> capable of summoning <a href=\"/index.php/Kraken\" title=\"Kraken\">krakens</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7